{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-321-swapping-counters","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 321: Kubadilisha Nafasi za Vihesabu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Vertikalni niz dužine $2n + 1$ ima $n$ crnih brojača postavljenih sa jedne strane i $n$ plavih brojača sa druge strane, razdvojene jednim praznim poljem u sredini. Na primer, kada je $n = 3$.</p>\n<img alt=\"tri polja sa crnim i plavim brojačima postavljenim na suprotnim stranama niza, razdvojeni jednim praznim poljem\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/swapping-counters-1.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Brojač može da se pomeri iz jednog polja u drugo (klizanjem) ili da preskoči drugi brojač (skokom), pod uslovom da je polje iza tog brojača prazno.</p>\n<img alt=\"miondoko inayoruhusiwa ya kihesabu\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/swapping-counters-2.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka $M(n)$ predstavlja minimalan broj poteza/koraka potrebnih za potpunu zamenu položaja brojača različitih boja; odnosno pomeranje svih crnih brojača na desnu stranu i svih plavih brojača na levu stranu.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da je $M(3) = 15$, što je takođe trougaoni broj.</p>\n<p>Ako formiramo niz vrednosti $n$ za koje je $M(n)$ trougaoni broj, prvih pet članova biće: 1, 3, 10, 22 i 63, a njihov zbir će biti 99.</p>\n<p>Tafuta jumla ya maneno arobaini ya kwanza ya mfululizo huu.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4ae1000cf542c50ffc0","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301978,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-321-swapping-counters"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function swappingCounters() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nswappingCounters();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>swappingCounters()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>2470433131948040</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(swappingCounters(), 2470433131948040);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-321-swapping-counters","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-322-binomial-coefficients-divisible-by-10","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-320-factorials-divisible-by-a-huge-integer","id":"5900f4ae1000cf542c50ffc0","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-321-swapping-counters"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}